// C4: Lookup Tables for Common EVM Operations
// Pre-computed tables for Keccak S-boxes, byte operations, and common patterns
// Stored in GPU constant memory for fast access
//
// Memory layout optimization:
// - Tables are stored in constant memory (cached on GPU)
// - 256-entry tables use 256 bytes each (efficient cache line utilization)
// - Tables are read-only, no bank conflicts

